TY  - JOUR
AU  - Pagan, Adrian
T1  - Two Stage and Related Estimators and Their Applications
PY  - 1986
Y1  - 1986/08/01
DO  - 10.2307/2297604
JO  - The Review of Economic Studies
JA  - Rev Econ Stud
VL  - 53
